me insensitive to the imposed\ntemperature jump and also agree with high-resolution simulations employing\nkinetic feedback.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2012 13:54:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2012 08:10:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2012 20:26:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2012 12:18:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
