nnections, can be inferred using the non-stationary model. Adding connections\nto this model slightly improves the agreement with the data for the probability\nof synchronous spikes but hardly affects the Zipf plot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2012 14:08:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2013 13:19:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-13"}
