ing both the soft and hard X-ray states, even when GX 339-4 is at\nits faintest optical state. We have conducted a timing analysis of the light\ncurve for the hard and soft states and find no evidence of a characteristic\ntimescale within the range of 4-230 days.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2012 15:26:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
